{{Top|leg}}
'''Thaissen crystals''' were found only on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Mimban/Legends|Mimban]]. The crystals glowed lightly in close proximity of a [[Force-sensitive/Legends|Force-sensitive]] individual—blue normally, but red when in close proximity of a [[darksider]]. The illumination was so faint that it was only visible to the naked eye in darkness.

The [[Palpatine/Legends|Emperor]] saw that these crystals could be used to create a [[Force detector]] so that common [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] troops could detect and hunt [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] as well. Over ten thousand Force-detectors were created to help hunt down and kill Force-sensitives. Fortunately for the remaining Jedi of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]], force-detectors were far from perfect. They could only be used to scan a single creature at a time, had a range of mere centimeters, and were not always accurate.

